					Dear Hagob,



					Please note  that the surveyor is currently waiting for appointment/location details to proceed with the survey.



					If a claim is being pursued, kindly provide the following at this stage:



					1)Contract with warehouse specifying who is responsible for maintenance of the warehouse;

					2)Contract with any maintenance company for periodic maintenance;

					3)Statement of the persons who first noticed the damage detailing when/how/where the rainwater entered;

					4)Invoices covering the claimed items;

					5)Formal valued Claim submitted to the responsible parties holding them liable.( including item no, description, unit price and total claim);

					6)Appointment and contact for the survey;

					7)Policy No. 31/MO/000421 is under FITRA INTERNATIONAL whereas the name changed to Chalhoub Group Arabia.  Could you please confirm the correct policy of last year in order to avoid wrong registration;

					8)Attached claim form duly completed in all respects.



					Awaiting your reply



					Thanks



					Firas Al Asaad

					Director – General Claims



					<image001.png>



					Nasco Saudi Arabia

					Real Building, 3rd Floor, Muhammad Marakshi Street, Az Zahra Dist,
					3705 Jeddah 23424-6269, KSA

